#~ "freely from its own equilibrium "
#~ "distribution. This term is <b>anti-"
#~ "Hebbian</b>: it weakens connections that "
#~ "are spuriously co-active in the "
#~ "model's own fantasies."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid "<b>Sculpting Energy: A Unifying Metaphor</b>"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The metaphor of <b>sculpting an energy"
#~ " landscape</b> provides a powerful unifying"
#~ " framework for understanding both Hopfield"
#~ " networks and Boltzmann machines:"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<b>Weights as sculpting tools</b>: Each "
#~ "weight $w_{ij}$ acts like a chisel "
#~ "that can either carve a valley (if"
#~ " $w_{ij} > 0$) or raise a ridge"
#~ " (if $w_{ij} < 0$) along the "
#~ "diagonal where $x_i = x_j$."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<b>Hebbian learning as an additive "
#~ "process</b>: Each stored pattern adds a"
#~ " new depression to the landscape, "
#~ "creating a new attractor basin."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<b>Boltzmann learning as a corrective "
#~ "process</b>: By comparing data correlations"
#~ " to model correlations, the learning "
#~ "algorithm not only adds basins where "
#~ "data lies but also <b>fills in "
#~ "spurious basins </b>that the model has"
#~ " invented."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This energy-centric view will recur "
#~ "throughout the remainder of this "
#~ "tutorial. The restricted Boltzmann machine "
#~ "(RBM), deep belief networks, and even"
#~ " modern energy-based models all share"
#~ " this <b>fundamental perspective</b>: learning"
#~ " is the process of shaping an "
#~ "energy function so that desirable "
#~ "configurations are assigned low energy "
#~ "and undesirable configurations are assigned"
#~ " high energy."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid "<b>Summary</b>"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<b>Hebbian learning</b> is a local, "
#~ "biologically plausible rule: <em>neurons that"
#~ " fire together, wire together</em>."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<b>Hebbian learning sculpts the energy "
#~ "landscape</b> by creating basins of "
#~ "attraction at the locations of stored"
#~ " patterns."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Pure Hebbian learning suffers from "
#~ "<b>spurious minima</b>, <b>limited capacity</b>, "
#~ "and <b>catastrophic forgetting</b>."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <b>Boltzmann machine learning rule</b> "
#~ "generalizes Hebb's principle by subtracting"
#~ " model correlations from data correlations,"
#~ " providing a principled way to shape"
#~ " the energy landscape to match a "
#~ "probability distribution."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The metaphor of <b>energy sculpting</b> "
#~ "unifies the learning principles of "
#~ "Hopfield networks and Boltzmann machines, "
#~ "and extends to modern deep generative"
#~ " models."
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The previous section introduced the "
#~ "Hopfield network as a dynamical system"
#~ " whose state evolves to minimize an"
#~ " energy function. The weights of the"
#~ " network determine the shape of this"
#~ " energy landscape, where the valleys "
#~ "are located, how deep they are, "
#~ "and how steep the walls between "
#~ "them. The question then arises: **how"
#~ " should these weights be set so "
#~ "that the energy landscape encodes useful"
#~ " memories?**> The answer lies in a"
#~ " remarkably simple and biologically "
#~ "plausible principle proposed by Canadian "
#~ "psychologist Donald Hebb in 1949. The"
#~ " **Hebbian learning rule**, often "
#~ "summarized as *\"neurons that fire "
#~ "together, wire together,\"* provides a "
#~ "local mechanism by which neural activity"
#~ " sculpts the global energy function. "
#~ "This section explores the mathematical "
#~ "connection between Hebbian synaptic "
#~ "modification and the shaping of an "
#~ "energy landscape, establishing the "
#~ "foundational learning principle that carries"
#~ " forward into the Boltzmann machine."
#~ msgstr ""

